{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2058, "height": 2846, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "冠。岂彰寿亭之勋，不借梨园子弟乎？爰鸠工庇材，经营于龙见、火见，图庆于昏中。定约计百金有奇，而节税之华、丹腹之美，不数月而增辉矣。公之输财好施，类如是。宜宰尹乡先生嘉许，而不置是。岂不可以求垂不朽乎！然公性恬退，谓功仅累黍，何敢言镌勒贞珉。而村舍乡邻等，深嘉其功，属余为文，余曰：黄冈竹楼、超然台榭，犹皆传其姓字。兰亭不序，则右军不传矣！微君等言，余亦不忍其湮没也。且无以为将来劝矣。因不辞陋，爰笔而为之记。", "block_bbox": [302, 254, 1868, 627], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "邑廪膳生员孟玺撰生员孟陈尧书", "block_bbox": [396, 645, 849, 755], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "天", "block_bbox": [395, 780, 759, 886], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "内有胞兄允会照应\n\n附：早春游东堂沟一律\n\n共步深椒禅，春迟翠尚微。疏枝饶古趣，叠嶂列重围。\n\n醉把乡携犹，崤倾杜办肥。不才惭落帽，强伴咏而归。\n\n芮见龙山西柴万盛号三义号杨万盛号赵如松王者相张永年杜口口\n杜进忠杜如桃杜从仁杜廷俊杜奉天监生杜承天杜文章仝立\n大清乾隆伍拾壹年岁次丙午菊月吉旦石匠宁大德\n", "block_bbox": [390, 915, 1741, 1354], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三八一", "block_bbox": [126, 2145, 180, 2257], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "皇清处士杜公墓", "block_bbox": [392, 1434, 702, 1478], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公讳朝宦，字公绅，邑北下营村人，口口□□□口□，居行三，孝友成性，耕读传家，配郭氏，口口淑媛德闲佳妇口口口祥庆口家□矣。子三人、孙三人、会孙七、元孙四，□□绳绳，方兴未艾，□口公之夫妇寿终□□合葬于村东北。至嘉庆庚申口之子俱已去世，孙学□与曾孙有口等恐日久莫辨，因伐石志墓，永垂不朽云。\n", "block_bbox": [304, 1501, 1222, 2017], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "龙飞嘉庆五年三月口口", "block_bbox": [395, 2038, 840, 2082], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "孙学纯口□口□学海有□曾孙有德有□有口有□有祥有泰元孙永清永利永福永成", "block_bbox": [393, 2102, 1096, 2282], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：碑在洛宁县河底镇下营村门外，当石凳、吃饭桌用。2009年3月与杜君安查访拍照整理。\n", "block_bbox": [306, 2303, 1220, 2476], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "农\n處\n福\n房", "block_bbox": [1274, 1407, 1869, 2582], "block_id": 10, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9820058345794678, "coordinate": [1274.6318359375, 1407.378662109375, 1869.10791015625, 2582.574951171875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9750415086746216, "coordinate": [304.0517578125, 1501.674072265625, 1222.9110107421875, 2017.856689453125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9620232582092285, "coordinate": [302.569580078125, 254.85110473632812, 1868.12646484375, 627.12255859375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9363045692443848, "coordinate": [306.1904296875, 2303.0888671875, 1220.89404296875, 2476.64794921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8696451187133789, "coordinate": [395.5574951171875, 780.5792846679688, 759.477294921875, 886.1577758789062]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8129014372825623, "coordinate": [392.3157653808594, 1434.8289794921875, 702.4420166015625, 1478.4454345703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6717801094055176, "coordinate": [396.1552734375, 645.5596923828125, 849.7574462890625, 755.3782958984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6438548564910889, "coordinate": [395.0146484375, 2038.1295166015625, 840.913330078125, 2082.85791015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.597395122051239, "coordinate": [394.6146240234375, 976.6920776367188, 835.563720703125, 1020.9409790039062]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5776753425598145, "coordinate": [393.1351318359375, 2102.02880859375, 1096.8765869140625, 2282.35400390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0