口□，居行三，孝友成性，耕读传家，配郭氏，口口淑媛德闲佳妇口口口祥庆口家□矣。子三人、孙三人、会孙七、元孙四，□□绳绳，方兴未艾，□口公之夫妇寿终□□合葬于村东北。至嘉庆庚申口之子俱已去世，孙学□与曾孙有口等恐日久莫辨，因伐石志墓，永垂不朽云。\n\n\n\n龙飞嘉庆五年三月口口\n\n孙学纯口□口□学海有□曾孙有德有□有口有□有祥有泰元孙永清永利永福永成\n\n注：碑在洛宁县河底镇下营村门外，当石凳、吃饭桌用。2009年3月与杜君安查访拍照整理。\n\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1274_1407_1869_2582.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"28%\" /></div>\n", "isStart": false, "isEnd": false, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_1274_1407_1869_2582.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//d579443f-0185-4527-9050-435a80362f77/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1274_1407_1869_2582.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A26Z%2F-1%2F%2F0b36b5d4318210abab771906789efaea6d0f64f22617638d257027e034799104"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//d579443f-0185-4527-9050-435a80362f77/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A27Z%2F-1%2F%2Fb313f14e39b0152116ad671fe9379b2b6e2e7ed3335baab3a65de442fd9054c6", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//d579443f-0185-4527-9050-435a80362f77/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A28Z%2F-1%2F%2F12ba66c8e339bbd190258e51cbf5b3000030ddb32c49b9ed94654729d623c167", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//d579443f-0185-4527-9050-435a80362f77/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A28Z%2F-1%2F%2F7d33176327e833a6fe6430a67d1f469d515c7f9d3b502c76754c4e86b100e238", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//d579443f-0185-4527-9050-435a80362f77/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqr